name: I love the autumn 02
description:
I love autumn so much, because I was born in autumn, a crazy person who never changes, the same person who listens to a song so much to hate its rhythm.
‏The same person whom everyone thinks is very tough and tough but breaks with a poke, the one who is the best support for everyone but never had a shoulder to rely on.
‏the one who has a lot to say but has no words, the one whose moments of silence are the most noisy moments of this life.
‏If you are born in autumn, you will repeat  mistake many times because you look at peaple’s hearts.
‏when you are born in fall, everyone is stranger to you.
‏If you are born in autumn, your presence will be me.
‏born in autumn means me, the same person you know, a genteel madam.
